{"tid":1284514,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂 – (半夢半醒) 20小時慢煮豬肋骨","createTime":"2019-07-04T08:00:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T16:39:19.000Z","uid":30742,"like":54,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"61a01dc13e46785fa055d604f3e64ae79b9fb6d0","tid":1284514,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T08:00:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kkH9LOv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkkH9LOv.jpg&h=f5bb6299&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VXWbeGR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVXWbeGR.jpg&h=039b19d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qrzfzCyhvVA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqrzfzCyhvVA&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFIwESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=0e27c152\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qrzfzCyhvVA</a>  <br />\n之前一直準備影相的事 <br />\n<br />\n之後掛住發夢都無咩心情煮飯剪片 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但之前儲落既就襯呢幾日半夢半醒攪攪佢 <br />\n<br />\n呢個之前試左兩次做比唔同既朋友食，評價都唔錯！ <br />\n一咬就骨肉分離但又唔會柴既sousvide ribs加上惹味bbq醬 <br />\n好難唔好食！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n夢醒了一定要再做！  <br />\n(將來大家一齊醒！我整比你地食，所以大家都要努力發夢！唔好自己醒！）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n圖文食譜: <a href=\"https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2019/07/20-20-hours-sous-vide-pork-ribs-with.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.com%2F2019%2F07%2F20-20-hours-sous-vide-pork-ribs-with.html&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFIwESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=eead9beb\" target=\"_blank\">https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2019/07/20-20-hours-sous-vide-pork-ribs-with.html</a>   <br />\n<br />\nFacebook專頁 : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http